1. class_predictions passed through softmax, so it is in [0,1], (converted model works on PC), image size is 300 on my model,

  2. I am using floating point model

  3. NUM_DETECTIONS=10 in *.java

  4. my label.txt start with "background"

  5. when I change max_detections, max_classes_per_detection paramaters othen than 5, 2, apk crashes
    I also set:
    new_output.attr['_output_quantized'].CopyFrom(attr_value_pb2.AttrValue(b=False)) in append_postprocessing_op function.
    and
    Tensor("raw_outputs/box_encodings:0", shape=(1, 1917, 4), dtype=float32)
    Tensor("raw_outputs/class_predictions:0", shape=(1, 1917, 21), dtype=float32)
    Tensor("anchors:0", shape=(4, ?), dtype=float32)
